

Like we calculate cve score by cvss metrics based on CIA,privacy,attack vector, easiness of the attack. Similarly I have proposed the scores of permissions based on these metrics.


NAME	SCORE
android.permission.BACKUP	10                    - confidentiality 

android.permission.DUMP	5     
android.permission.INTERACT_ACROSS_USERS	3               
android.permission.INTERACT_ACROSS_USERS_FULL	4
android.permission.INTERNET	7                             -CIA
android.permission.WAKE_LOCK	2           
android.permission.CAMERA_SEND_SYSTEM_EVENTS  	10        - privacy
android.permission.CAMERA_DISABLE_TRANSMIT_LED	9   
android.permission.BLUETOOTH_ADMIN	10  -                   confiden       - 
android.permission.KILL_BACKGROUND_PROCESSES	9          - availability of other apps 
android.permission.CLEAR_APP_USER_DATA	10                 - 
android.permission.ACCESS_MOCK_LOCATION	6
android.permission.ACCESS_NOTIFICATION_POLICY	5
android.permission.BATTERY_STATS	6
android.permission.NFC	2
